{
  "texts": [
    "The number of Ae.",
    "tauschii subpopulations that contributed to the hexaploid wheat D genome does not necessarily reflect the number of independent hybridization events, because the Ae.",
    "tauschii line that contributed the D genome may have already been admixed.",
    "To infer the minimal number of hybridizations that gave rise to the extant wheat D genome, we assessed the number of haplotypes present at any given position in the wheat D genome.",
    "We used Chinese Spring as a reference and identified 50-kb windows showing no identity-by-state across the 126 hexaploid wheat landraces for which WGS data were available."
  ]
}